sources.title: Silver Fleet The
sources.description: From IMDB http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0036356/ Jaap van Leyden is in charge of a shipyard in newly occupied Holland. At first he collaborates with the Germans because it is the easiest course to follow. Later a child's rhyme reminds him of his patriotic duty, but how best to resist the Nazis without endangering his wife and fellow workers ? Stars: Ralph Richardson, Googie Withers and Esmond Knight Writers: Vernon Sewell, Gordon Wellesley
